title: Stunning Russell Blockbuster + Fantasy Fallout, Q&A - Fantasy Football Podcast for 3/10
description:
Russell Wilson to the Broncos?! The Fantasy Footballers are back with another exciting episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason react to the blockbuster Russell Wilson trade! What is the fantasy football fallout for the Broncos and Seahawks? Plus NFL News including Aaron Rodgers & Davante Adams back with the Packers, and a handful of players franchise tagged. All this, plus listener questions answered! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for March 10th, 2022.

The 2022 UDK is available for pre-order at UltimateDraftKit.com -- Get instant access to the Dynasty Pass with the UDK+
